        <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;2048---岛石版&#34;&gt;2048 &amp;ndash;岛石版&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;一键安装部署:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    docker run --name 2048-nginx -d -p 8080:80 bruce996/2048
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;A small clone of &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.veewo.a1024&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;1024&lt;/a&gt;, based on &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://saming.fr/p/2048/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Saming&amp;rsquo;s 2048&lt;/a&gt; (also a clone).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Made just for fun. &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://gabrielecirulli.github.io/2048/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Play it here!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The official app can also be found on the &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gabrielecirulli.app2048&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Play Store&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/2048-by-gabriele-cirulli/id868076805&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;App Store!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;contributions&#34;&gt;Contributions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/iirelu/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Anna Harren&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/sigod&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;sigod&lt;/a&gt; are maintainers for this repository.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Other notable contributors:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/TimPetricola&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;TimPetricola&lt;/a&gt; added best score storage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/chrisprice&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;chrisprice&lt;/a&gt; added custom code for swipe handling on mobile&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/marcingajda&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;marcingajda&lt;/a&gt; made swipes work on Windows Phone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/mgarciaisaia&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;mgarciaisaia&lt;/a&gt; added support for Android 2.3&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Many thanks to &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/rayhaanj&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;rayhaanj&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/Mechazawa&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Mechazawa&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/grant&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;grant&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/remram44&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;remram44&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/ghoullier&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;ghoullier&lt;/a&gt; for the many other good contributions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;screenshot&#34;&gt;Screenshot&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That screenshot is fake, by the way. I never reached 2048 :smile:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;contributing&#34;&gt;Contributing&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Changes and improvements are more than welcome! Feel free to fork and open a pull request. Please make your changes in a specific branch and request to pull into &lt;code&gt;master&lt;/code&gt;! If you can, please make sure the game fully works before sending the PR, as that will help speed up the process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can find the same information in the &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/gabrielecirulli/2048/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;contributing guide.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;license&#34;&gt;License&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2048 is licensed under the &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/gabrielecirulli/2048/blob/master/LICENSE.txt&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;MIT license.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;donations&#34;&gt;Donations&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I made this in my spare time, and it&amp;rsquo;s hosted on GitHub (which means I don&amp;rsquo;t have any hosting costs), but if you enjoyed the game and feel like buying me coffee, you can donate at my BTC address: &lt;code&gt;1Ec6onfsQmoP9kkL3zkpB6c5sA4PVcXU2i&lt;/code&gt;. Thank you very much!&lt;/p&gt;
